<!--
  ScreensaverScene - dashboard-only scene used when the channel is
  launched as a Roku screensaver (RunAsScreenSaver = true).

  Shares Dashboard.brs with MainScene. No disclaimer, no settings UI,
  no key handling - Roku dismisses the screensaver on any key press.

  Account configuration is done in the regular channel (MainScene);
  accounts are read from the shared roRegistrySection("nightscout").
-->
